Pure Storage is Simple and Automated, the Most efficient architecture, mission-critical reliability support, and Customer consumption model architecture design of the Pure Storage Flash Array, the all-flash storage array for every enterprise. Learn about Flash Array's hardware and software design, metadata, and data reduction features (deduplication, compression, pattern removal, and thin provisioning).


The dashboard is a macro view of your entire storage array. 
On the left-hand side, we have the health of the array> 
all recent alerts below
On the right-hand side, we have a capacity analysis.
This shows your total provision capacity as well as data reduction ratios with and without them provisioning
	We also have a total utilization percentage up here in the green.
	Below capacity, we have real-time and historical analytics
	for latency IOPs and bandwidth.


